OL,3,CSchool crossing patrols to wear
OL,4,Ccameras after lollipop lady punched
OL,6,FLollipop ladies and men will begin
OL,7,Fwearing security cameras after a spate
OL,8,Fof incidents which saw one of them
OL,9,Fpunched and two children involved in
OL,10,Fhit and run incidents.
OL,12,FThe school crossing patrols in
OL,13,FRochdale will be given body-worn
OL,14,Fcameras in a trial to protect children
OL,15,Fand the patrol staff.
OL,17,FThe local council says it hopes the
OL,18,Fmove will deter "hostile and dangerous
OL,19,Fdrivers".
