OL,3,CSchool crossing patrols to wear
OL,4,Ccameras after lollipop lady punched
OL,6,FCouncillor Shah Wazir, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor facilities and highways at
OL,8,FRochdale Borough Council, said: "I'm
OL,9,Fappalled by these incidents.
OL,11,F"That's why we're not hesitating to
OL,12,Fput extra protection measures in place
OL,13,Fand send the message out that this
OL,14,Fbehaviour is completely unacceptable."
OL,16,FThe decision comes after a four-year-
OL,17,Fold boy was clipped by a car which
OL,18,Ffailed to stop at a crossing on
OL,19,FHartley Lane and Daventry Road on 16
OL,20,FMay.
