OL,4,Ccameras after lollipop lady punched
OL,6,FThe following week, on 21 May, a car
OL,7,Fqueuing in traffic on Kiln Lane,
OL,8,FMilnrow reversed into an 11-year-old
OL,9,Fgirl, as she was crossing the road.
OL,11,FThe driver was attempting to beat the
OL,12,Ftraffic by cutting through a nearby
OL,13,Festate.
OL,15,FFortunately, neither child was
OL,16,Fseriously injured.
