OL,3,CSchool crossing patrols to wear
OL,4,Ccameras after lollipop lady punched
OL,6,FOn Thursday 6 June, a motorist
OL,7,Fassaulted a school crossing patrol
OL,8,Fofficer as she was setting up on the
OL,9,Fcorner of Edenfield Road and Churchill
OL,10,FStreet.
OL,12,FThe male driver pulled up in his car,
OL,13,Fgot out and punched the woman, leaving
OL,14,Fher with a mark on her face, before
OL,15,Fdriving off. The staff member has
OL,16,Frecovered and returned to work.
OL,18,FAll three incidents have been reported
OL,19,Fto Greater Manchester Police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
