OL,4,Ccameras after lollipop lady punched
OL,6,FCllr Wazir said: "This aggression and
OL,7,Fimpatience from drivers has now led to
OL,8,Ftwo young children being clipped by
OL,9,Fcars and culminated in a physical
OL,10,Fattack on one of our members of staff
OL,11,Fwhile she was doing her job.
OL,13,F"We're extremely fortunate that none
OL,14,Fof these incidents left somebody with
OL,15,Fserious injuries, or worse."
OL,17,FThe council will trial the cameras at
OL,18,Fcrossing points where officers report
OL,19,Fhigh levels of fail to stop activity.
