OL,3,CSchool crossing patrols to wear
OL,4,Ccameras after lollipop lady punched
OL,6,FIt is hoped the move will ensure that
OL,7,Fevidence can be gathered to support
OL,8,Fprosecutions.
OL,10,FIt is an offence to continue to fail
OL,11,Fto stop at a school crossing from the
OL,12,Fmoment the lollipop stick is lifted to
OL,13,Findicate that they are ready to step
OL,14,Finto the road.
OL,16,FFailure to stop can incur penalty
OL,17,Fpoints and a fine of up to #1,000.
OL,19,FThe council says it reports every
OL,20,Fincident to police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
